name: XENOBIONT: 0_Stasis
description: A collaborative series between Samuele Bonaffino (@hubstruct) and Joshua Bagley (@gengeomergence). Xenobiont is a study of the interaction between Differential Growth and Physarum Polycephalum simulations. Each image of this series is a 1/1 single edition NFT, available exclusively here on hicetnunc. Made completely with code written in Processing and P5js. 2048x2048 pixels.
